          About this item

          • MODERN STYLE : Revamp your space with these stylish and sleek Modern Geometrical Curtains, perfect for adding a contemporary touch to any room.
          • PERFECT FIT: Designed for 7-feet Door, Each package contains 2 curtains, each measuring Width 46 inches X Length 84 inches (1.16M X 2.13M) or (4Ft X 7Ft).
          • SUPERIOR QUALITY: Made with 150 GSM polyester fabric, these curtains are durable, light-weight and semi-transparent, letting in the perfect amount of natural light.
          • QUICK INSTALLATION: With the eyelet rings, these curtains can be set up easily in no time and enhance your room decor instantly.
          • EASY CARE: Simply wash them separately with mild detergent. Avoid bleaching and dry them immediately to maintain their beautiful appearance.

          What is in the box?

        • 2 Door Curtains

          • Product Description

          HOME SIZZLER

          “Home Sizzler “ is a young and fastest growing brand in ‘Ready-made Curtains and Home Furnishing’ category. It brings design, color and flair together to create a beautiful interior and reasonably priced to fit your budget for your home or workplace.

          Home Sizzler Polyester Curtain

          Make your home look gorgeous by bringing home these exclusively define modern and contemporary style curtains. Home Sizzler curtains are made of 100% high quality polyester which has a natural resistance to shrinkage and wrinkles making them easy to maintain. It’s gives a much desired sassy look.

          Geometrical Panel

          • Offering a quality curtain with geometric printed pattern.
          • Pattern provide a stylish and unique design.
          • This gives trendy look and redefines your decor

          Polyester Material

          • Crafted from 100% polyester.
          • Composition adds up to the longevity of these curtains.
          • Makes maintenance a hassle – free affair.
          • Fade resistant even after multiple washes.

          High Quality Eyelets

          • Each curtain has 8 silver coated eyelets for an elegant look.
          • Rust resistant eyelets.
          • Eyelet holes are large enough for most rods in the market it easy to move the curtains along the rods.

          Dimensions

          Dimensions of each curtain

          • Window - 5 feet: Width 116 CM X Length 153 CM (4 Feet X 5 Feet)
          • Door - 7 feet: Width 116 CM X Length 213 CM (4 Feet X 7 Feet)
          • Long Door - 9 feet: Width 116 CM X Length 274 CM (4 Feet X 9 Feet)

          Care Instructions

          • Normal hand wash or machine wash.
          • Wash with normal detergent.
          • Do not bleach.
          • After washing dry it immediately

          Transparency Guide

          • Curtain Transparency / Opacity: Semi-Transparent (Light Filtering)
          • Ideal for filtering out some natural light.
          • Product Quality: 150 GSM
